{"tid":1959523,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"而家開始唔係牛市，亦唔係熊市，係牛熊市","createTime":"2020-04-05T12:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T16:37:36.000Z","uid":125976,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"624cd88ccd5194d676d6e3903846416a79930b01","tid":1959523,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:48:02.000Z","msg":"成個經濟都傻撚咗<br />\n班二世祖玩負利率鳩印銀紙<br />\n資產市場可能都癲埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據量子力學嘅「薛定諤的貓」理論，市場喺你落盤之前係「牛熊疊加態」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ER1yfon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FER1yfon.jpg&h=69d331a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你落盤買入滙豐、煤氣𠵱類舊經濟股嘅時候，你就會觀測到市場係「熊市」<br />\n<br />\n而當你落盤買入騰訊、藥明生物𠵱類新經濟股嘅時候，你就會觀測到市場係「牛市」<br />\n<br />\n而當你決定一股不留嘅時候，市場又變返「牛熊疊加態」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2902da2290936568ad76cc20061801059c0d64","tid":1959523,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"牛熊龍疊加態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0971af0175eeba358fe08792f48e6c4cbff5768b","tid":1959523,"uid":159435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:52:02.000Z","msg":"喺股市咁多年<br />\n我覺得好多時係去到你幾乎頂唔順嘅狀態就會轉勢<br />\n所以最好止蝕前諗一諗<br />\n可能個turning point好快就到<br />\n未必有需要喺最低位沽貨"},{"pid":"92593ef18cc4246f12afc74b6d1b7569d92f8335","tid":1959523,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0971af0175eeba358fe08792f48e6c4cbff5768b","tid":1959523,"uid":159435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:52:02.000Z","msg":"喺股市咁多年<br />\n我覺得好多時係去到你幾乎頂唔順嘅狀態就會轉勢<br />\n所以最好止蝕前諗一諗<br />\n可能個turning point好快就到<br />\n未必有需要喺最低位沽貨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"strong hold?"},{"pid":"3ad7ea7e358f34711b410100888a9cd56a9479b5","tid":1959523,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0971af0175eeba35